citations:
    citation-affc-brienne-viii:
        source: source-affc
        properties:
            locator: "Brienne VIII"
            text_from_source: "This is an evil dream, she thought. But if she were dreaming, why did it hurt so much?"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Brienne, Podrick, and Hyle Hunt are captured by the Brotherhood Without Banners now led by Lady Stoneheart. Brienne is brought before the undead Catelyn Stark and given the choice: kill Jaime Lannister or hang. She refuses and screams a word as the rope jerks tight — the chapter ends on this cliffhanger."
